overview:
Phone-Numbers-UK.com provides its users with virtual UK Phone Numbers.

You can register a phone number of your choice and suitable pricing plan, then choose how you would like the call to be handled. Calls can be directed to a mobile number a land line number, fax line, or voice mail. The are also options of VoIP and fax to email and you can access both faxes and voice mail from your computer online.

Our number ranges include: 0207 numbers, 0800 numbers, 0844 numbers, 0845 numbers, 0870 numbers, 0871 numbers, 07-D numbers, 07-K numbers, 07-PN2 numbers and Gold UK numbers!
